<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="25">CHINA. Jiangxi Province: Anyuan County, Sanbaishan Forest Park, on fallen angiosperm branch, 15 Aug. 2016, He 4401 (holotype, BJFC 023842!).</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
